-What?
-I'm sorry, okay?

00:00:09.241 --> 00:00:11.444
-It -- It's okay. We love you.
-We love you.

00:00:11.477 --> 00:00:13.146
And we just want to help.
Okay?

00:00:13.179 --> 00:00:15.248
I had to go in your room
because I smelled

00:00:15.281 --> 00:00:17.717
what I thought could
only be the stench of death.

00:00:17.750 --> 00:00:19.752
But then I later discovered
it was an unfinished

00:00:19.785 --> 00:00:21.554
everything bagel
with cream cheese,

00:00:21.587 --> 00:00:23.856
which -- no judgment --
is way worse.

00:00:23.889 --> 00:00:25.558
Who doesn't finish
an everything bagel?

00:00:25.591 --> 00:00:26.425
Right?

00:00:26.459 --> 00:00:28.628
I am not playing
this little game, okay?

00:00:28.661 --> 00:00:30.029
And don't go
into my room again.

00:00:30.062 --> 00:00:32.065
-Jaimé.
-Jaimé. Jaimé, wait. Hold on.

00:00:32.098 --> 00:00:34.033
Hold on a second.
Come here.

00:00:34.066 --> 00:00:37.103
Here, babe. It's okay.

00:00:52.751 --> 00:00:54.053
I think it's going well.

00:00:54.086 --> 00:00:55.688
-Really good.
-Yeah.

00:01:02.561 --> 00:01:04.397
Mmm.

00:01:04.430 --> 00:01:09.068
♪♪

00:01:09.101 --> 00:01:12.138
Hold on. Ilana, are you
using the same cheese grater

00:01:12.171 --> 00:01:14.140
on the cheese that
you're using on your feet?

00:01:14.173 --> 00:01:17.009
Yeah. Okay. Let's dig in.
Welcome back.

00:01:17.042 --> 00:01:18.811
Okay, but just so you know,
it's not that

00:01:18.844 --> 00:01:20.813
I'm not still mad
about you going into my room.

00:01:20.846 --> 00:01:23.116
Not cool. Very not cool.
-Totally not cool.

00:01:23.149 --> 00:01:25.485
I'm glad that you're
honoring your instincts.

00:01:25.518 --> 00:01:27.487
And good for you
for setting boundaries.

00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:29.689
I just want you to
explore your feelings

00:01:29.722 --> 00:01:31.324
in a judgment-free zone,
okay?

00:01:31.357 --> 00:01:32.926
This is a safe space.

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:35.995
Well, not literally safe.

00:01:36.028 --> 00:01:38.030
How about we start with
looking at the most common

00:01:38.063 --> 00:01:40.333
causes of hoarding and see if
you connect with any of them?

00:01:40.366 --> 00:01:42.135
Now, I don't want to
put words in your mouth,

00:01:42.168 --> 00:01:45.671
but hoarding often develops
as a coping mechanism

00:01:45.704 --> 00:01:48.307
for a feeling
of a lack of control.

00:01:48.340 --> 00:01:50.143
Does that
resonate with you?

00:01:50.176 --> 00:01:51.911
W-Well, obviously,
before I became a citizen,

00:01:51.944 --> 00:01:53.980
you know, I was always
so anxious about my status.

00:01:54.013 --> 00:01:56.215
And, you know, you feel
this lack of control.

00:01:56.248 --> 00:01:57.817 line:85%
-Very powerless, you know?

00:01:56.248 --> 00:01:57.817
-Mm.

00:01:57.850 --> 00:01:59.485
That's really when it started
to all pile up.

00:01:59.518 --> 00:02:00.820
Abbi: Okay, I-I'm sorry
to interrupt.

00:02:00.853 --> 00:02:03.156
I'm still feeling very
uncomfortable in general,

00:02:03.189 --> 00:02:04.924
and I'm also
starting to feel ill,

00:02:04.957 --> 00:02:06.559
probably because
I've been eating cheese

00:02:06.592 --> 00:02:07.994
that's mixed in
with your heel skin.

00:02:08.027 --> 00:02:09.295
I'm -- I'm so sorry
that my emotions

00:02:09.328 --> 00:02:10.897
are making you
this uncomfortable.

00:02:10.930 --> 00:02:13.966
I love you and support you.
This is about Ilana's feet.

00:02:13.999 --> 00:02:15.968
One moment, please.
Abbi, relax.

00:02:16.001 --> 00:02:18.304
I put the grater in Barbicide
after I use it on my feet.

00:02:18.337 --> 00:02:19.739
Do you think I'm an idiot?

00:02:19.772 --> 00:02:21.741
Barbicide?

00:02:21.774 --> 00:02:25.344
Okay, so, what I'm sensing
is that the hoarding...

00:02:25.377 --> 00:02:27.947
...provides a sense of comfort
in times of stress.

00:02:27.980 --> 00:02:30.416
It's gotten a lot worse lately,
to be honest, and I don't...

00:02:30.449 --> 00:02:31.751
I don't know why, 'cause I --

00:02:31.784 --> 00:02:33.653
I really have been
so happy with you.

00:02:33.686 --> 00:02:35.154
I know you have, babe.

00:02:35.187 --> 00:02:37.557
You know, I often
encounter in my work

00:02:37.590 --> 00:02:41.260
people struggling with the
duality of relationships.

00:02:41.293 --> 00:02:42.662
You know, maybe
there's something

00:02:42.695 --> 00:02:44.497
about this relationship,

00:02:44.530 --> 00:02:48.067
even if it's going dopely,
that's causing anxiety.

00:02:48.100 --> 00:02:50.403
I'm sorry, but, Ilana, do I
have to go to the hospital?

00:02:50.436 --> 00:02:51.637
Oh, my God.

00:02:51.670 --> 00:02:53.739
Okay, you are wasting
Jaimé's hour.

00:02:53.772 --> 00:02:56.842
Okay? This is so unprofessional!
I'll handle it, okay?

00:02:56.875 --> 00:02:58.912
[ Indistinct arguing ]

00:03:47.359 --> 00:03:49.495
Okay, dude,
just be honest with me.

00:03:49.528 --> 00:03:51.864
Did I or did I not eat
your foot cheese?

00:03:51.897 --> 00:03:54.367
What part of "I put the cheese
grater in Barbicide

00:03:54.400 --> 00:03:56.435
before it touches the cheese"
do you not understand?

00:03:56.468 --> 00:03:58.004
And not for nothing,
you're probably

00:03:58.037 --> 00:03:59.905
lactose-intolerant 'cause
you're an Ashkenazi Jew.

00:03:59.938 --> 00:04:01.307
Or maybe you didn't
know that. Okay?

00:04:01.340 --> 00:04:03.276
And have you never sucked
on a couple toes before?

00:04:03.309 --> 00:04:05.077
-I have sucked on toes.
-Really?

00:04:05.110 --> 00:04:06.779
-Yeah.
-Because you're lucky, girl.

00:04:06.812 --> 00:04:09.782
A lot of people pay good money
for my foot shavings.

00:04:09.815 --> 00:04:11.684
They do?

00:04:11.717 --> 00:04:13.519
Ooh! Look at these two.

00:04:13.552 --> 00:04:15.988
Am I good, or am I good?
[ Chuckles ]

00:04:16.021 --> 00:04:18.424
All right, that is about all
the time we have for this week.

00:04:18.457 --> 00:04:20.259
Actually, we went a little bit
over, but that's okay.

00:04:20.292 --> 00:04:22.762
I want to thank you for making
me confront my hoardiness,

00:04:22.795 --> 00:04:24.964
because it made me see
that I was just putting it

00:04:24.997 --> 00:04:26.866
as a barrier for the next
step in our relationship.

00:04:26.899 --> 00:04:29.001
That's the best thing
a therapist can hear.

