00:05:01.700 --> 00:05:04.437
You were right -- I need to
stop self-sabotaging myself.

00:05:04.470 --> 00:05:06.739
Now I need to take the next step
with my boyfriend.

00:05:06.772 --> 00:05:08.808
I see -- One therapy session,
and now you're cured!

00:05:08.841 --> 00:05:11.243
-Okay, great.
-Not a real therapy session.

00:05:11.276 --> 00:05:13.212
Please! It wasn't.
I'm sorry. It's not.

00:05:13.245 --> 00:05:15.281
Classic denial!
You are mental, bro!

00:05:15.314 --> 00:05:17.717
Abbi: Ilana, can I talk
to you for a second?

00:05:17.750 --> 00:05:19.585
Let me just talk to you
for a second over here. Okay.

00:05:19.618 --> 00:05:21.487
If this is about
the fuckin' foot cheese,

00:05:21.520 --> 00:05:23.422
-I swear to God, Abbi...
-No, listen, dude.

00:05:23.455 --> 00:05:25.624
I think you need to take
some of your own advice.

00:05:25.657 --> 00:05:28.561
