with you right now.

00:05:33.932 --> 00:05:35.501
I mean, him moving out
is a huge deal,

00:05:35.534 --> 00:05:37.403
and you're trying
to control him.

00:05:37.436 --> 00:05:39.438
You have to let him
live his own life.

00:05:39.471 --> 00:05:41.240
I said all that, huh?

00:05:41.273 --> 00:05:43.542
Yeah, you did.

00:05:43.575 --> 00:05:46.946
Hey, you guys. Fully sorry.
That was stupid.

00:05:46.979 --> 00:05:48.881
-It's okay.
-It's not about me.

00:05:48.914 --> 00:05:50.383
I am so sorry.
-Mm. It's all good.

00:05:50.416 --> 00:05:52.251
You know, this is
right for you guys.

00:05:52.284 --> 00:05:54.320
And you know what?
I think I've been scared

00:05:54.353 --> 00:05:57.056
